name: Cheesecake
description:
Oh, cheesecake... the most decadent of desserts.  The only choice you need to make is whether you prefer blueberry or cherry!

These approximately 1/2" charms come on a clear elastic necklace with silver clasp.

(Each charm is handmade and may not appear exactly as pictured.)

name: Pie Slices
description:
Mmmm, pie - perfect for any occasion.  If pie's your thing, we've got a slice for you!

Choose from apple, lemon meringue, chocolate cream, or pumpkin!

Each slice is approximately 3/4" and will come on a clear elastic necklace with silver clasp.

(Each charm is handmade and may not appear exactly as pictured.)

name: Hamburgers & Hot Dogs
description:
Who doesn't love a barbecue?  

Show your love of summer cook-outs with a hamburger or hot dog charm - grilled to perfection!  

These tiny grilled favourites come on a clear elastic necklace with silver clasp.

(Each charm is handmade and may not appear exactly as pictured.)

name: Peanut Butter & Jelly Sandwich
description:
Prefer a sandwich to sugary desserts?  Then this miniature peanut butter and jelly sandwich is perfect for you!

A little under 3/4" in size, this mini sandwich charm comes on a clear elastic necklace with silver clasp.

(Each charm is handmade and may not appear exactly as pictured.)

name: Cupcake Charm
description: Our personal favourite... cupcakes! Currently available in three delicious scents (or unscented!) with more options coming soon! This charm is fully customizable - choose your own cake flavor, icing colour, toppings, and scent from the options below, and then send an email to iAJcupcake@gmail.com with your selections. Cake Flavour Chocolate Brown Golden Vanilla Strawberry White Cake Icing Colour Pink Yellow Brown White Red Blue Green Purple Orange Toppings Rainbow Sprinkles Cherry Scent Chocolate Fudge French Vanilla Birthday Cake Unscented Please remember to email us with your selections!
